{"tid":1330941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新手和理非，想討論下柒婆的死穴","createTime":"2019-07-18T18:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T18:15:22.000Z","uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12a1512c4f0ee235d442965a616d775503ca26fb","tid":1330941,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:15:22.000Z","msg":"各位好，小弟新手一名，<br />\n仲要搞左好耐先註冊到連登。<br />\n絕非5毛or 25<br />\n<br />\n依幾個月，每次睇到電視都忍得好辛苦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜上有高堂下有妻兒，<br />\n所以冇辦法參加各位咁多個月嘅行動，<br />\n 本人好著深切嘅遺憾同後悔。<br />\n<br />\n不過再咁打落去，恐怕有傷亡，<br />\n一不小心有條狗死左，就柒婆贏番曬，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nor大吉利是，有巴打出事，更怕變堅暴動，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最重要係長期戰不嬲都對大家不利，<br />\n<br />\n所以柒婆都一直都狗縮，<br />\n一直拖到大家金魚腦上身，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又再一次忘記佢做過d咩野，<br />\n拖到大家的火自然熄滅，<br />\n<br />\n固此，小弟抖膽邀請各位入嚟討論一下，<br />\n柒婆的有無真正死穴，可以做到攻其必救之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}